{"tid":2198440,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★本屆議員完成任期可獲約滿酬金約70多萬元　延任再獲一筆酬金","createTime":"2020-09-11T10:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T12:32:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e5beffc3d11582f42f59001f43a2dbec3464f455","tid":2198440,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:55:11.000Z","msg":"立法會行政管理委員會決定，所有完成本屆立法會4年任期的議員，都可獲得約滿酬金，如果議員延任1年，下年度會再獲一筆約滿酬金。<br />\n<br />\n身兼行管會主席的立法會主席梁君彥期望，不同光譜的議員都留在議會，才能令議會發揮作用，又指如果議員打算離任，不應拖泥帶水，應該於9月30日前通知立法會，才可申領用作結束辦事處的開支，指現階段未有議員向立法會表明會離任。<br />\n<br />\n目前立法會議員月薪10萬1000元，完成任期後可獲15%的約滿酬金，約為70多萬元。梁君彥引述政府表示，不反對行管會靈活處理議員酬津安排。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549120-20200911.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549120-20200911.htm&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fsdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=804e6c54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549120-20200911.htm&h=037a9b32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549120-20200911.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d027ecc5fef65fcb780d0d6bd3c4b5a86938c014","tid":2198440,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2501d3fa68325967a95491c106955cb88c87f0","tid":2198440,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:59:32.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦<br />\n議員不嬲蝕住做 我地唔會貪筆錢"},{"pid":"61c2d04bb7ffccc9440258fcf4a9d3b5d8d4580c","tid":2198440,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid